Season Six Match
VENDETTA
Vendetta
HT: 5'6

AMI EMERSON
The Valkyrie

Lifetime record (0-1)

Number one ranked Vendetta takes on the best of the rookies for season six. Vendetta is being tested and tested early this year. Can any one stop her from being the first person to win the Championship twice?
Ami is big, strong and flexible with the desire and fight to win. She is being groomed for greatness. Her first match was with Ariel X and now she faces Vendetta. When we let her lose on the lower ranks, look out!
title: Vendetta (2-0)
